{"tid":1186434,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"仲有良知嘅北方人應該放棄中国，建立南方文明地區","createTime":"2019-06-05T02:39:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-30T14:28:35.000Z","uid":90735,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"cd23c789e66c7d9b7790c9d0b3cfbad7b1e7c4a3","tid":1186434,"uid":90735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T02:39:30.000Z","msg":"六四事件屠殺有良知嘅人，無人再敢公開爭取公義<br />\n面對頑固嘅殺人政權機器，普通人根本無可能改變<br />\n而且，中国依家問題係支那人太多，正常人散落各地單打獨鬥<br />\n<br />\n北邊嘅維權人士、有良知嘅人，應該放棄中国，南遷到廣東（唔好嚟香港）<br />\n透過生育，家庭教育，滲入教育系統，慢慢灌輸普世價值<br />\n教育呢個過程好慢，但假以時日，北邊同南邊文化差異漸大<br />\n<br />\n北邊嘅人互相掠奪自殘，並且受環境污染而早死<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZKwNSbb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZKwNSbb.gif&h=f58063a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n南邊嘅人互相扶持，休養生息，越來越多人支持平等、自由、公義、同理心，南邊嘅人慢慢就建立到身分認同，之後嘅嘢唔洗講啦<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/BSSpYPs.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBSSpYPs.gif&h=2ca456a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n講咗咁耐，北邊南邊嘅人差異化，其實對香港百利而無一害，南方文明地區成為香港嘅屏障<br />\n<br />\nok，我打完飛機喇，將呢個idea植入去北方嘅正常人係第一步而且係最難嘅一步"},{"pid":"7bd2bf07a8e642ebdf77f6309ac973fb62064b19","tid":1186434,"uid":90735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T03:20:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1228fb88832b4b55937a32d219773c07f28eeda","tid":1186434,"uid":90735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T07:10:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f548e92baa9a000c825296da5b94edb58e823d42","tid":1186434,"uid":151731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T07:15:05.000Z","msg":"係進化論啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d16a5e0b56d822993ca79e092ab62a700e3dab6","tid":1186